rms more green.=E2=80=9D</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">So from second principles, if you want to be a=
 climate investor, maybe you should invest=C2=A0<em>only=C2=A0</em>in coal =
companies,=C2=A0take over their boards and make them stop mining coal. <a h=
ref=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/33879916.258409/aHR0cH=
M6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMDItMjMvYnV5LXRoZ=
