r: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  There ar=
e some examples</a>. But there are some=C2=A0problems with this too. For on=
e thing, if you go around buying up coal companies, you raise the price of =
coal companies, lowering their cost of capital and incentivizing other peop=
le to get into the coal mining business so they can sell to you.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">For another thing, there is a <a href=3D"https=
://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/33879916.258409/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYm=
xvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMDUtMjMvdGhlLXNlYy1nb2VzLWFmd=
GVyLWdyZWVud2FzaGluZz9jbXBpZD1CQkQwMTAzMjRfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVt=
YWlsJnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9bmV3c2xldHRlciZ1dG1fdGVybT0yNDAxMDMmdXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPW1=
