hat does and doesn=E2=80=99t work.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Anyway here=E2=80=99s a good Bloomberg Green a=
rticle about <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/33879=
916.258409/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjQtMDEt=
