om-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">The=
 Horse, the Drone and the Epic Fight for Gambling Success</a>.=E2=80=9D I h=
ave not read it yet; I assume it=E2=80=99s about someone using drones to fr=
ont-run online bookmakers on horse races, though I suppose it is possible t=
hat it=E2=80=99s about someone using horses to front-run online bookmakers =
on drone races.</p>
